import React from 'react'
  import { MDXTag } from '@mdx-js/tag'
  

export default class MDXContent extends React.Component {
  constructor(props) {
    super(props)
    this.layout = null
  }
  render() {
    const { components, ...props } = this.props

    return <MDXTag
             name="wrapper"
             
             components={components}><MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`An MLS Membership.`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`subClassOf:`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="ul" components={components}>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul"><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="li" props={{"href":"https://schema.org/OrganizationRole"}}>{`https://schema.org/OrganizationRole`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`used on types (domain): `}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="ul" components={components}>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul">{`RealEstateOrganization`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul">{`RealEstateOffice`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul">{`RealEstateAgent`}</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`subPropertyOf:`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="ul" components={components}>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul">{`memberOf`}</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"examples"}}>{`examples`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="pre" components={components}><MDXTag name="code" components={components} parentName="pre" props={{"className":"language-yaml"}}>{`type: RealEstateAgent
memberOf:
-   
    type: MLSMembership 
    memberOf:
        type: MultipleListingService
        name: MLS Listings
    identifier: bruce.wayne
`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}><MDXTag name="strong" components={components} parentName="p">{`inverse example`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="pre" components={components}><MDXTag name="code" components={components} parentName="pre" props={{"className":"language-yaml"}}>{`type: MultipleListingService
name: MLS Listings
member:
-
    type: RealEstateAgent
    member:
    -
        type: RealEstateAgent
        identifier: bruce.wayne
`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
           </MDXTag>
  }
}
